_:N6a6184b1124d45518ab3905720bf4572 <http://schema.org/name> "Roddy Miller" .
_:N6a6184b1124d45518ab3905720bf4572 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Roddy joined Sellafield Ltd in March 2022 as head of retrievals value stream.</p>\n\n<p>Prior to joining Sellafield Ltd, he enjoyed a diverse career with over 20 years’ experience leading project and programme portfolios and business transformations across Europe, Middle East, and Asia. </p>\n\n<p>This experience has been gained through a range of senior and executive roles supporting nuclear and other highly regulated sectors.</p>\n\n<p>Roddy was appointed Chief Operating Officer in 2024.</p>\n" .
